      <lg xml:id="Aink136">
<l>nāṇilai maṉṟa pāṇa nīyē</l>
<l>kōṇē rilaṅkuvaḷai nekiḻtta</l>
<l>kāṉalan tuṟaivaṟkuc collukup pōyē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>Oh bard, only you have no shame! -- </l>
    <l>You who utters words to the man from the ghat</l>
      <l>With a seashore grove</l>
      <l>Who made loose my bunch of fine, shining bangles.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
